{"type":"text","timestamp":1782532266679,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","part":{"id":"prt_f07339f34001zY42JcsVb6Frje","messageID":"msg_f07338e4f001ixn2YUgZuT8HEN","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","type":"text","text":"The expected `014-routing-benchmark` directory is present but currently empty except an empty `design-interface/` child; no benchmark file is available there to cite. IвҖҷll record that as a corpus gap and use the user-provided Mode A score as an operator-supplied datum, clearly labeled.","time":{"start":1782532251444,"end":1782532266677},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_079a1a7959041e02016a3f489b6fd481918fec2da8904ea9b0","phase":"commentary"}}}}
