{"type":"text","timestamp":1782532348048,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","part":{"id":"prt_f07350eed001BUGUjuAbvVByLR","messageID":"msg_f0734f950001s3vDNoAGzlx7X7","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","type":"text","text":"The live md-generator has already incorporated several earlier recommendations: authoring-boundary and source-of-truth router now exist, `--fast` interaction/default-output drift is corrected in the nested path, and v3 deterministic emitters are wired. The improvement focus is shifting from вҖңadd missing boundary docsвҖқ to routing discoverability, UX wrappers around the pipeline, schema/playbook consistency, and a non-SaaS exemplar.","time":{"start":1782532345581,"end":1782532348046},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_05ddbbb8ad583f90016a3f48f994b88191a336aa6508f2c0e6","phase":"commentary"}}}}
