{"type":"text","timestamp":1782532390641,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","part":{"id":"prt_f0735bdb1001gwFh2soxpLXUqs","messageID":"msg_f073583cf001yFIFOrufYdGerR","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","type":"text","text":"The declared spec subfolder exists only as a research lineage path; `spec.md`, `plan.md`, `tasks.md`, and `resource-map.md` are absent at that subfolder level. IвҖҷll record `folder_state: no-spec` in the lineage outputs and continue, because the requested artifact root is present and writable.","time":{"start":1782532390321,"end":1782532390639},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0f9f392428e18d6d016a3f492639c081949e75420682665337","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782532433600,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_sYCMIApTklY7tGyWo2P8Uh7V","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-design/graph-metadata.json","offset":1,"limit":260},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-design/graph-metadata.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"schema_version\": 2,\n3:   \"skill_id\": \"sk-design\",\n4:   \"family\": \"sk-code\",\n5:   \"category\": \"design\",\n6:   \"importance_tier\": \"important\",\n7:   \"edges\": {\n8:     \"depends_on\": [],\n9:     \"enhances\": [\n10:       {\n11:         \"target\": \"sk-code\",\n12:         \"weight\": 0.6,\n13:         \"context\": \"Design output (direction, foundations, motion, audit findings, DESIGN.md) feeds sk-code implementation in the detected code surface\"\n14:       }\n15:     ],\n16:     \"siblings\": [\n17:       {\n18:         \"target\": \"sk-code\",\n19:         \"weight\": 0.5,\n20:         \"context\": \"Design-and-build peer in the sk-code family; sk-design owns taste, sk-code owns implementation\"\n21:       },\n22:       {\n23:         \"target\": \"sk-code-review\",\n24:         \"weight\": 0.4,\n25:         \"context\": \"Reviews implementation quality after design and build work converge\"\n26:       }\n27:     ],\n28:     \"conflicts_with\": [],\n29:     \"prerequisite_for\": []\n30:   },\n31:   \"manual\": {\n32:     \"depends_on\": [],\n33:     \"related_to\": [\n34:       \"sk-code\",\n35:       \"sk-code-review\",\n36:       \"mcp-figma\",\n37:       \"mcp-open-design\"\n38:     ]\n39:   },\n40:   \"domains\": [\n41:     \"design\",\n42:     \"ui-design\",\n43:     \"visual-design\",\n44:     \"design-systems\",\n45:     \"motion-design\",\n46:     \"design-audit\",\n47:     \"design-tokens\"\n48:   ],\n49: 