{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782533139567,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c98ffe3IWN2NyShq3kW9","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_lu45gywlwPokhHny1cl9dlfH","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/005-md-generator/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-state.jsonl","offset":1,"limit":20},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/005-md-generator/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\"type\":\"config\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-xmcn5n\",\"generation\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"lineageLabel\":\"gpt55fast\",\"executor\":\"cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/005-md-generator\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/005-md-generator/research/lineages/gpt55fast\",\"topic\":\"Improve sk-design md-generator efficiency, usefulness, UX, tooling, references, assets, and routing\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"folder_state\":\"no-spec\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:00:00Z\"}\n2: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"newInfoRatio\":0.92,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Map live md-generator contract and path reality\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Established the actual nested packet path, phase model, and hard fidelity constraints that bound all recommendations.\",\"summary\":\"The active mode is .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator, not the older flat md-generator path. The skill is a three-phase extract/write/validate pipeline with v3 Style Reference output and a strict measured-value contract.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/SKILL.md:23-29\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:12-15\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:221-305\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:263-270\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:01:00Z\"}\n3: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"newInfoRatio\":0.64,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Reconcile prior corpus recommendations with current live state\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Separated already-implemented recommendations from remaining useful improvements.\",\"summary\":\"The previous reference-expansion run ranked md-generator as the leanest mode and recommended authoring_boundary plus a source-of-truth card. Both now exist in the live skill, so the new improvement surface is not more boundary prose; it is routing, setup/tooling UX, schema/playbook alignment, and exemplar diversity.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/research.md:115-125\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/authoring_boundary.md:18-28\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/assets/source_of_truth_router_card.md:16-74\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:02:00Z\"}\n4: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"newInfoRatio\":0.55,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Assess tooling and setup friction\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Found a concrete setup blocker and a UX seam between scripts that affects efficiency.\",\"summary\":\"The backend README and SKILL setup instructions depend on cd backend && npm install, but the live nested backend contains package-lock.json and no package.json. The pipeline also exposes separate scripts rather than a guided run command that can preflight setup, run extraction, build the write prompt, validate, and emit a report.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:276-307\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/README.md:38-58\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/README.md:88-107\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/package-lock.json:1-26\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/cli.ts:7-18\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/cli.ts:43-53\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:03:00Z\"}\n5: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.43,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Assess routing and benchmark evidence\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Connected the operator-supplied Mode A score to narrow md-generator aliases and missing benchmark artifacts.\",\"summary\":\"The user supplied Mode A score 76/100, but the expected routing benchmark directory is empty in this checkout. Live routing metadata has broad parent signals and md-generator aliases for extraction/generation, but it underspecifies validation-only, report/preview/proof, example-study, style-reference, and DESIGN.md update intents.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/mode-registry.json:63-73\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/graph-metadata.json:49-65\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/graph-metadata.json:67-116\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:32-40\",\"operator-supplied datum: Mode A md-generator score equals 76/100; benchmark file absent under 014-routing-benchmark\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:04:00Z\"}\n6: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.34,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Assess usefulness, examples, and manual-testing burden\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Identified exemplar skew and a heavy manual playbook that lacks a small release-smoke lane.\",\"summary\":\"The skill has 13 manual scenarios and strong evidence requirements, but most users need a quick happy-path smoke test first. The four examples are all developer/SaaS-adjacent, supporting the prior recommendation for a fifth non-SaaS aesthetic exemplar. A focused release-smoke script/report would improve operator UX without weakening the full playbook.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:23-40\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:63-75\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:131-141\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/examples/stripe/DESIGN.md:1-6\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/examples/vercel/DESIGN.md:1-6\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/examples/linear/DESIGN.md:1-6\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/examples/supabase/DESIGN.md:1-6\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:05:00Z\"}\n7: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.06,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Prioritize improvements and define do-not list\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly synthesis: no new major evidence class appeared after routing, setup, examples, and prior-corpus reconciliation were covered.\",\"summary\":\"Priority order converged on restoring backend setup viability, expanding md-generator routing/benchmark coverage, adding a guided pipeline UX, aligning docs/playbooks to emitted schema, adding one non-SaaS exemplar, and keeping forward-authoring plus second-backend ideas out of scope.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/extraction_workflow.md:46-60\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/troubleshooting.md:41-63\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/quality_checklist.md:23-30\",\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/external/stitch-skill.md:17-25\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/authoring_boundary.md:86-99\",\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/research.md:158-176\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:06:00Z\"}\n8: {\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"converged\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"iteration\":6,\"stopReason\":\"converged\",\"totalIterations\":6,\"newInfoTrend\":[0.92,0.64,0.55,0.43,0.34,0.06],\"qualityGuards\":{\"sourceDiversity\":true,\"focusAlignment\":true,\"noSingleWeakSource\":true,\"questionsAnswered\":\"5/5\"},\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:07:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-xmcn5n\",\"generation\":1}\n\n(End of file - total 8 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-xmcn5n\",\"generation\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"lineageLabel\":\"gpt55fast\",\"executor\":\"cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/005-md-generator\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/005-md-generator/research/lineages/gpt55fast\",\"topic\":\"Improve sk-design md-generator efficiency, usefulness, UX, tooling, references, assets, and routing\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"folder_state\":\"no-spec\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T00:00:00Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"newInfoRatio\":0.92,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Map live md-generator contract and path reality\",\"noveltyJustification\":\"Established the actual nested packet path, phase model, and hard fidelity constraints that bound all recommendations.\",\"summary\":\"The active mode is .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator, not the older flat md-generator path. The skill is a three-phase extract/write/validate pipeline with v3 Style Reference output and a strict measured-value contract.\",\"sources\"